# Trivy misconfig findings intentionally accepted for this image.
#
# DS002 — "Image user should not be 'root'"
#   The container runs Xvfb, x11vnc, XFCE, and Chromium services that
#   require root (or complex capability grants that are harder to audit).
#   Capabilities are already dropped in docker-compose.yml (cap_drop: ALL
#   + minimal cap_add) and no-new-privileges is set.  Adding a non-root
#   USER is tracked as a future hardening item.
DS002

# DS014 — "RUN using 'wget' or 'curl' with pipe"
#   NodeSource provides no alternative install mechanism for their APT
#   repository setup script.  The script is fetched over HTTPS with TLS
#   certificate verification (-fsSL).
DS014
